column5: going up first week of june does anybody have good places to get walleyes and coordinaces would really appriciate it thanks much

Are you talking about going to Andy Myers lodgeon Eagle Lake west of Dryden. The owners nameis Steve Herbeck. If this is the place you arestaying we have fished out of that lodge for 4-5years. Could mark a map and send to you if youwant.E-mail me your address.
